/>\n<br />\n見網上講號碼轉移，只係轉資料"},{"pid":"f7d29ff4975c364b3d21512e76e5b9e6c3e7c82d","tid":95821,"uid":19517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"搭單問iTunes 個備份<br />\n點樣確保個備份冇損毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次整機前備份左（都有6x gb) 之後回復到大半個陣就話備份損毀 restore 唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通次次備份完要用第二部機試一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a124f62fffa82ad9d3f7394bea206053baa1e98a","tid":95821,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>icloud 可唔可以完整備份所有野去新機？<br />\n<br />\n已經係 icloud 揀晒所有野 ＋備份<br />\n<br />\n本機儲存話我用左 34GB <br />\n但而家 icloud 只係用左 22GB<br />\n<br />\n咁重有 1X GB 去左邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApps 係你restore 個陣會自己下載返 <br />\niCloud 只會backup 入面既資料</blockquote><br />\n唔該，岩岩見證左<br />\n<br />\n不過而家遇到第二個好似解決唔到既問題<br />\n舊機用開既號碼張SIM 已無左，好似唔可以照係新機用舊No. <br />\n<br />\n見網上講號碼轉移，只係轉資料</blockquote><br />\n唔明<br />\n用舊number做乜"},{"pid":"730fb5f793e1887cb9b9939a11d6cd79c5e601eb","tid":95821,"uid":50331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>icloud 可唔可以完整備份所有野去新機？<br />\n<br />\n已經係 icloud 揀晒所有野 ＋備份<br />\n<br />\n本機儲存話我用左 34GB <br />\n但而家 icloud 只係用左 22GB<br />\n<br />\n咁重有 1X GB 去左邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApps 係你restore 個陣會自己下載返 <br />\niCloud 只會backup 入面既資料</blockquote><br />\n唔該，岩岩見證左<br />\n<br />\n不過而家遇到第二個好似解決唔到既問題<br />\n舊機用開既號碼張SIM 已無左，好似唔可以照係新機用舊No. <br />\n<br />\n見網上講號碼轉移，只係轉資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n號碼跟張 SIM 喎，轉咗新 SIM 就用 新 SIM 嘅號碼"}]}